{"tid":929174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食環真係科學忍者隊，今次用夜視鏡同人工智能捉老鼠","createTime":"2018-12-05T11:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T11:46:13.000Z","uid":389,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b9be26bad5238bc9e455171907d8fb114e0af46e","tid":929174,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:25:42.000Z","msg":"上回：<br />\n<img src=\"https://lih.kg/489945\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flih.kg%2F489945&h=25cf47a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxc7zvr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcxc7zvr.png&h=ea526059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鼠患問題一直影響各區，食環署截至今年九月，共清理二萬三百隻死鼠，及捕獲一萬一千八百隻活鼠。<br />\n<br />\n為加強滅鼠成效，食環署正考慮使用各種新科技應用，包括使用電力推動的捕鼠器，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">亦正探討使用夜視攝錄技術及人工智能科技</span></span>，可有助分析鼠隻密度及活動情況，從而制定針對性的控鼠滅鼠方案。另外，署方亦正測試新的控蚊方法，透過雌蚊將調節劑帶到水體中，令孑孓不能孵化成成蚊。<br />\n<br />\n針對「食住行」制定方案<br />\n<br />\n食環署昨日向立法會提交文件，講解防治蚊患及鼠蚊工作。文件指出，署方上年五月起在各區進行為期兩個月的目標小區滅鼠行動，透過從老鼠「食」、「住」、「行」三方面防治鼠患，並在今年六月完成第一期行動後，隨即針對鼠患嚴重地區，如深水埗、旺角、東區進行評估，在上月八日起開展第二期行動。<br />\n<br />\n食環署亦正研究使用各種新科技應用加強滅鼠成效，包括使用新型捕捉器，透過以電力推動的捕鼠器，可不須人手啟動及經常檢查，但由於可能誤捕或誤傷其他小動物，所以較適合於室內及沒有其他小動物的環境下使用。<br />\n<br />\n食環署表示，除進行捕鼠器及殺鼠劑的測試外，亦會研究改善鼠患指數調查的方法，以更準確反映各區的鼠患分布情況。<br />\n<br />\n文件同時指出，正探討使用夜視攝錄技術及人工智能科技了解鼠患情況，分析鼠患問題及其嚴重程度，例如鼠隻密度及活動情況，從而制定針對性的控鼠滅鼠方案。針對蚊患方面，食環署正測試新的控蚊方法，以雌蚊作為媒介，將控制蚊子生長的調節劑帶到各水體中，使水體中的孑孓不能孵化成成蚊。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1363806/#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1363806%2F%23&d=OessR97wZcg0TsqPXAmbnAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7b7c0cee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1363806%2F%23&h=e3b6ae58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1363806/#</a>"},{"pid":"d3fc8751a265087d75531028eac4e1109c2fd662","tid":929174,"uid":389,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:26:48.000Z","msg":"夜視捉鼠食環佬想像圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CcVH7RU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCcVH7RU.png&h=d242d229&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"690abd78fc4aace062ba7a2af8f7c51a8f56aba0","tid":929174,"uid":20066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:27:10.000Z","msg":"創科局筆錢去左食環<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7a25ee61661f1a60f2d3ffcb2424ef83a15b83","tid":929174,"uid":389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"690abd78fc4aace062ba7a2af8f7c51a8f56aba0","tid":929174,"uid":20066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:27:10.000Z","msg":"創科局筆錢去左食環<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:27:55.000Z","msg":"估唔到香港天網首次應用就係比食環用"},{"pid":"55efd78b72f6b8fcf5e052f8bbc55ff13ed4f9af","tid":929174,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"正喔。。。等我即刻報名入食環試下套新裝備先"},{"pid":"9578c00058f6f74f278e7533510f5f83f3209899","tid":929174,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktWwgMf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktWwgMf.png&h=0413b886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可傳漢坦病、最新發現有機會令人染上戊型肝炎的老鼠，任何人都怕，只是「米奇」們愛夜間出沒，要找不易。食物環境衞生署指，在鼠患嚴重地點安裝夜視鏡，有助分析鼠患及其嚴重程度，例如鼠隻密度及活動情況，從而制訂針對性的控鼠滅鼠方案，夜視鏡監察系統所得資料及數據，亦有助分析及評估控鼠滅鼠措施的成效。不過，要大規模應用有關技術於恒常滅鼠工作，還需克服各項技術和環境問題，該署現正考慮試驗應用有關技術，並會評估廣泛使用的可行性。 <br />\n<br />\n對於引入創新技術進行防治蟲鼠工作，該署強調一直有積極研究及進行測試，評估各種方法在香港適用情況，一般而言，這些科技產品可分成四大類別，包括除害劑、捕捉器、利用基因技術方法及夜視鏡監察系統。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181107/bkn-20181107151855149-1107_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181107%2Fbkn-20181107151855149-1107_00822_001.html&d=OessR97wZcg0TsqPXAmbnAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0ccb7e16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181107/bkn-20181107151855149-1107_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f99cc04547ce42bea660e57b8f605be3fcc9acc4","tid":929174,"uid":52276,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a92zeBd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa92zeBd.jpg&h=b314d558&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0309f2ea29a324c206f28c179cd968d68ea6915","tid":929174,"uid":39838,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fivegallonideas.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/bucket-mouse-trap-with-dowel-peanut-butterr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffivegallonideas.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F04%2Fbucket-mouse-trap-with-dowel-peanut-butterr.jpg&h=67f6a309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母用夜視鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98cbf0329cf510e6eb5b5ef51ce238e4c02efbae","tid":929174,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hpM8i3D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhpM8i3D.png&h=86af52a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c2741608518a27e10a9f0074126d4d8f98efc79","tid":929174,"uid":22566,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxc7zvr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcxc7zvr.png&h=ea526059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢匿草叢做乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 伏老鼠？"},{"pid":"87045dff1097319cdbd4781d69c5d3270780a29e","tid":929174,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c2741608518a27e10a9f0074126d4d8f98efc79","tid":929174,"uid":22566,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxc7zvr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcxc7zvr.png&h=ea526059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢匿草叢做乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 伏老鼠？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:42:37.000Z","msg":"果次好似伏人"},{"pid":"150fd65acaa61dfa1ecae0944ac8d56ee4315b41","tid":929174,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktWwgMf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktWwgMf.png&h=0413b886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可傳漢坦病、最新發現有機會令人染上戊型肝炎的老鼠，任何人都怕，只是「米奇」們愛夜間出沒，要找不易。食物環境衞生署指，在鼠患嚴重地點安裝夜視鏡，有助分析鼠患及其嚴重程度，例如鼠隻密度及活動情況，從而制訂針對性的控鼠滅鼠方案，夜視鏡監察系統所得資料及數據，亦有助分析及評估控鼠滅鼠措施的成效。不過，要大規模應用有關技術於恒常滅鼠工作，還需克服各項技術和環境問題，該署現正考慮試驗應用有關技術，並會評估廣泛使用的可行性。 <br />\n<br />\n對於引入創新技術進行防治蟲鼠工作，該署強調一直有積極研究及進行測試，評估各種方法在香港適用情況，一般而言，這些科技產品可分成四大類別，包括除害劑、捕捉器、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">利用基因技術</span></strong>方法及夜視鏡監察系統。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181107/bkn-20181107151855149-1107_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181107%2Fbkn-20181107151855149-1107_00822_001.html&d=OessR97wZcg0TsqPXAmbnAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0ccb7e16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181107/bkn-20181107151855149-1107_00822_001.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/2/27/Mimic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F2%2F27%2FMimic.jpg&h=608d9489&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"714dff624b53cddcc2e8c39dc8c8975c36f46d5e","tid":929174,"uid":117602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c2741608518a27e10a9f0074126d4d8f98efc79","tid":929174,"uid"